  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585310/extras/03a392a07b0fc24654e3ac3ef9bfe6cf.poster.avif?t=1762490898\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585310/extras/03a392a07b0fc24654e3ac3ef9bfe6cf.webm?t=1762490898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585310/extras/03a392a07b0fc24654e3ac3ef9bfe6cf.mp4?t=1762490898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle! Exciting! A perfect combination of Tower Defense and TPS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More weapons! Now includes explosive weapons like rocket launchers and the Gatling gun – even more thrilling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features both single-player mode and up to 4-player co-op multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four new distinct classes to choose from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five different maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your stats through off-battle enhancements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape aboard Lao Da's helicopter after surviving enough rounds!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585310/extras/03a392a07b0fc24654e3ac3ef9bfe6cf.poster.avif?t=1762490898\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585310/extras/03a392a07b0fc24654e3ac3ef9bfe6cf.webm?t=1762490898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585310/extras/03a392a07b0fc24654e3ac3ef9bfe6cf.mp4?t=1762490898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle! Exciting! A perfect combination of Tower Defense and TPS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More weapons! Now includes explosive weapons like rocket launchers and the Gatling gun – even more thrilling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features both single-player mode and up to 4-player co-op multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four new distinct classes to choose from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five different maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your stats through off-battle enhancements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape aboard Lao Da's helicopter after surviving enough rounds!</p></li></ul>",
